                                                                  3231 1451
 Optical model                                                    3231 1451
 - SCAT2 code used for spherical OM parameterization.             3231 1451
 - For neutrons OM by Wilmore-Hodgson was modified to reproduce   3231 1451
   total cross section for natural Ge.                            3231 1451
   ----------                                                     3231 1451
   U=47.76-0.228*E-0.00118*E**2                                   3231 1451
   W=9.17-0.053*E                                                 3231 1451
   V_so=7.0                                                       3231 1451
