 Level densities and discrete levels                              3231 1451
 - Gilbert-Cameron level densities were used with energy dependent3231 1451
   a-parameter proposed by Ignatyk.                               3231 1451
   The asymptoticvalue of the a-parameter is calculated by the    3231 1451
