   based on the 1998 version of the ENSDF database.               3231 1451
                                                                  3231 1451
 Other parameters and tuning                                      3231 1451
 - ECIS03 with DWBA option was used to account for direct         3231 1451
   contribution to low lying 2+ and 3- discrete levels in (n,n'). 3231 1451
   Deformation parameters were taken from work of (p,p') analysis 3231 1451
   [Ke92].                                                        3231 1451
 - Preequilibrium components were calculated using the following  3231 1451
   options: Multistep direct and multistep compound models with   3231 1451
   default parameters for neutron channel, exciton model with     3231 1451
   angular momentum coupling (DEGAS) for proton and gamma         3231 1451
   channels, cluster emissin model by Iwamoto and Harada (PCROSS) 3231 1451
   for alpha channel                                              3231 1451
 - Gamma-ray strength function of modified Lorentzian version 1   3231 1451
   (MLO1) by Plujko in RIPL-2 was used.                           3231 1451
 - Asymptotic level density parameter for Ga-72 was multiplied by 3231 1451
   1.2 to reproduce experimental data.                            3231 1451
